157:<script type="text/javascript" src="/hrd/Framework/little2.function.js"></script>

<body id="body_classevaluationtable_competencyevaluator_list">
	<input type="hidden" name="empId" value="F39BA5B7-0F25-492B-AB6B-7FFC132EB351" />
	<div id="tab1">

		<table id="classevaluationtable_competencyevaluator_list"></table>
		<div id="classevaluationtable_competencyevaluator_pager1"></div>
	</div>
</body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("classevaluationtable_competencyevaluator_list", {
			url : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyevaluator/pageList.html',
			postData : {
				'competency_type' : 'manage',
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             'No',
			             '工號',
			             '姓名',
			             '任職資訊',
			             '配重權重',
			             '評鑑關係',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:55 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'No' ,
			             name:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             width:40 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'工號' ,
			             name:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'姓名' ,
			             name:'Level' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Level' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'任職資訊' ,
			             name:'Evaluator' ,
			             width:200 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Evaluator' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'配重權重' ,
			             name:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑關係' ,
			             name:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 250,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#classevaluationtable_competencyevaluator_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "classevaluationtable_competencyevaluator_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyevaluator/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'classevaluationtable_competencyevaluator_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyevaluator/',
			add2:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"增加評鑑關係",
				bclass:"add2",
				body:"",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete2:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"Delete評鑑關係",
				bclass:"delete2",
				body:"/hrd/competency/course/edit.html",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			:{
				name:"",
				title:"",
				bclass:"",
				body:"",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
		});

	});

function button_obj()
{
	this.title = "Default";



}


</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("classevaluationtable_competencyevaluator_list", {
			url : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyevaluator/pageList.html',
			postData : {
				'competency_type' : 'manage',

			             '姓名',

			             '配重權重',
			             '評鑑關係',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:55 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'No' ,
			             name:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             width:40 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'工號' ,
			             name:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'姓名' ,
			             name:'Level' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Level' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'任職資訊' ,
			             name:'Evaluator' ,
			             width:200 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Evaluator' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'配重權重' ,
			             name:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑關係' ,
			             name:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 250,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#classevaluationtable_competencyevaluator_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "classevaluationtable_competencyevaluator_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyevaluator/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'classevaluationtable_competencyevaluator_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyevaluator/',
			add2:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"增加評鑑關係",
				bclass:"add2",
				body:"",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete2:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"Delete評鑑關係",
				bclass:"delete2",
				body:"/hrd/competency/course/edit.html",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			:{
				name:"",
				title:"",
				bclass:"",
				body:"",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
		});

	});

function button_obj()
{
	this.title = "Default";

			             hidden:false ,

			grid : "",

			gridId : 'classevaluationtable_competencymanage_list',

	<input type="hidden" name="empId" value="F39BA5B7-0F25-492B-AB6B-7FFC132EB351" />
	<div id="tab1">

		<table id="classevaluationtable_competencypro_list"></table>
		<div id="classevaluationtable_competencypro_pager1"></div>
	</div>
</body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("classevaluationtable_competencypro_list", {
			url : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencypro/pageList.html',
			postData : {
				'competency_type' : 'manage',
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             'No',
			             '職能',
			             '等級',
			             '評鑑者',
			             '評鑑方法',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:0 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'No' ,
			             name:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             width:30 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'職能' ,
			             name:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'等級' ,
			             name:'Level' ,
			             width:50 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Level' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑者' ,
			             name:'Evaluator' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Evaluator' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑方法' ,
			             name:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 230,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#classevaluationtable_competencypro_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "classevaluationtable_competencypro_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencypro/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'classevaluationtable_competencypro_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencypro/',
			add:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"新增評鑑關係",
				bclass:"add",
				body:"/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyedit/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			edit:{
				name:"編輯",
				title:"編輯評鑑關係",
				bclass:"edit",
				body:"/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyedit/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"刪除評鑑關係",
				bclass:"delete",
				body:"/hrd/function/delete/delete_competency_model.php",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
		});

	});

function button_obj()
{
	this.title = "Default";



}


</script>

157:<script type="text/javascript" src="/hrd/Framework/little2.function.js"></script>

<body id="body_competency_basislist_list">
	<input type="hidden" name="empId" value="F39BA5B7-0F25-492B-AB6B-7FFC132EB351" />
	<div id="tab1">

		<table id="competency_basislist_list"></table>
		<div id="competency_basislist_pager1"></div>
	</div>
</body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("competency_basislist_list", {
			url : '/hrd/competency/basislist/pageList.html',
			postData : {
				'competency_type' : 'manage',
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             'No',
			             '職能項目名稱',
			             '定義',
			             '權重',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:25 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'No' ,
			             name:'CompetencyID' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'center' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'CompetencyID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'職能項目名稱' ,
			             name:'CompetencyTitle' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'CompetencyTitle' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'定義' ,
			             name:'CompetencyDefinition' ,
			             width:450 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'CompetencyDefinition' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'權重' ,
			             name:'Weight' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Weight' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 450,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#competency_basislist_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "competency_basislist_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/competency/basislist/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'competency_basislist_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/competency/basislist/',
			search:{
				name:"查詢",
				title:"查詢BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"search",
				body:"/hrd/competency/setting/edit.html",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			add:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"新增BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"add",
				body:"/hrd/competency/setting/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			edit:{
				name:"編輯",
				title:"編輯BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"edit",
				body:"/hrd/competency/setting/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"刪除BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"delete",
				body:"/hrd/function/delete/delete_competency_model.php",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			import:{
				name:"匯入",
				title:"匯入BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"import",
				body:"/hrd/import/xls/edit.html",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
		});

	});

function button_obj()
{
	this.title = "Default";



}


</script>

	<input type="hidden" name="empId" value="F39BA5B7-0F25-492B-AB6B-7FFC132EB351" />
	<div id="tab1">

		<table id="classevaluationtable_competencypro_list"></table>
		<div id="classevaluationtable_competencypro_pager1"></div>
	</div>
</body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("classevaluationtable_competencypro_list", {
			url : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencypro/pageList.html',
			postData : {
				'competency_type' : 'manage',
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             'No',
			             '職能',
			             '等級',
			             '評鑑者',
			             '評鑑方法',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:0 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'No' ,
			             name:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             width:30 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'職能' ,
			             name:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'等級' ,
			             name:'Level' ,
			             width:50 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Level' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑者' ,
			             name:'Evaluator' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Evaluator' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑方法' ,
			             name:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 230,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#classevaluationtable_competencypro_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "classevaluationtable_competencypro_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencypro/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'classevaluationtable_competencypro_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencypro/',
			add:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"新增評鑑關係",
				bclass:"add",
				body:"/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyedit/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			edit:{
				name:"編輯",
				title:"編輯評鑑關係",
				bclass:"edit",
				body:"/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyedit/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"刪除評鑑關係",
				bclass:"delete",
				body:"/hrd/function/delete/delete_competency_model.php",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
		});

	});

function button_obj()
{
	this.title = "Default";



}


</script>

157:<script type="text/javascript" src="/hrd/Framework/little2.function.js"></script>

<body id="body_competency_basislist_list">
	<input type="hidden" name="empId" value="F39BA5B7-0F25-492B-AB6B-7FFC132EB351" />
	<div id="tab1">

		<table id="competency_basislist_list"></table>
		<div id="competency_basislist_pager1"></div>
	</div>
</body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("competency_basislist_list", {
			url : '/hrd/competency/basislist/pageList.html',
			postData : {
				'competency_type' : 'manage',
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             'No',
			             '職能項目名稱',
			             '定義',
			             '權重',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:25 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'No' ,
			             name:'CompetencyID' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'center' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'CompetencyID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'職能項目名稱' ,
			             name:'CompetencyTitle' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'CompetencyTitle' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'定義' ,
			             name:'CompetencyDefinition' ,
			             width:450 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'CompetencyDefinition' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'權重' ,
			             name:'Weight' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Weight' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 450,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#competency_basislist_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "competency_basislist_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/competency/basislist/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'competency_basislist_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/competency/basislist/',
			search:{
				name:"查詢",
				title:"查詢BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"search",
				body:"/hrd/competency/setting/edit.html",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			add:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"新增BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"add",
				body:"/hrd/competency/setting/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			edit:{
				name:"編輯",
				title:"編輯BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"edit",
				body:"/hrd/competency/setting/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"刪除BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"delete",
				body:"/hrd/function/delete/delete_competency_model.php",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			import:{
				name:"匯入",
				title:"匯入BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"import",
				body:"/hrd/import/xls/edit.html",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
		});

	});

function button_obj()
{
	this.title = "Default";



}


</script>

	<input type="hidden" name="empId" value="F39BA5B7-0F25-492B-AB6B-7FFC132EB351" />
	<div id="tab1">

		<table id="classevaluationtable_competencypro_list"></table>
		<div id="classevaluationtable_competencypro_pager1"></div>
	</div>
</body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("classevaluationtable_competencypro_list", {
			url : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencypro/pageList.html',
			postData : {
				'competency_type' : 'manage',
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             'No',
			             '職能',
			             '等級',
			             '評鑑者',
			             '評鑑方法',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:0 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'No' ,
			             name:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             width:30 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'職能' ,
			             name:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'等級' ,
			             name:'Level' ,
			             width:50 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Level' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑者' ,
			             name:'Evaluator' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Evaluator' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑方法' ,
			             name:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 230,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#classevaluationtable_competencypro_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "classevaluationtable_competencypro_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencypro/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'classevaluationtable_competencypro_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencypro/',
			add:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"新增評鑑關係",
				bclass:"add",
				body:"/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyedit/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			edit:{
				name:"編輯",
				title:"編輯評鑑關係",
				bclass:"edit",
				body:"/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyedit/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"刪除評鑑關係",
				bclass:"delete",
				body:"/hrd/function/delete/delete_competency_model.php",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
		});

	});

function button_obj()
{
	this.title = "Default";



}


</script>

157:<script type="text/javascript" src="/hrd/Framework/little2.function.js"></script>

<body id="body_competency_basislist_list">
	<input type="hidden" name="empId" value="F39BA5B7-0F25-492B-AB6B-7FFC132EB351" />
	<div id="tab1">

		<table id="competency_basislist_list"></table>
		<div id="competency_basislist_pager1"></div>
	</div>
</body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("competency_basislist_list", {
			url : '/hrd/competency/basislist/pageList.html',
			postData : {
				'competency_type' : 'manage',
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             'No',
			             '職能項目名稱',
			             '定義',
			             '權重',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:25 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'No' ,
			             name:'CompetencyID' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'center' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'CompetencyID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'職能項目名稱' ,
			             name:'CompetencyTitle' ,
			             width:100 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'CompetencyTitle' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'定義' ,
			             name:'CompetencyDefinition' ,
			             width:450 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'CompetencyDefinition' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'權重' ,
			             name:'Weight' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Weight' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 450,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#competency_basislist_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "competency_basislist_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/competency/basislist/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'competency_basislist_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/competency/basislist/',
			search:{
				name:"查詢",
				title:"查詢BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"search",
				body:"/hrd/competency/setting/edit.html",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			add:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"新增BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"add",
				body:"/hrd/competency/setting/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			edit:{
				name:"編輯",
				title:"編輯BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"edit",
				body:"/hrd/competency/setting/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"刪除BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"delete",
				body:"/hrd/function/delete/delete_competency_model.php",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			import:{
				name:"匯入",
				title:"匯入BasisCompetency",
				bclass:"import",
				body:"/hrd/import/xls/edit.html",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
		});

	});

function button_obj()
{
	this.title = "Default";



}


</script>

		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("classevaluationtable_competencymanage_list", {
			url : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencymanage/pageList.html',
			postData : {
				'competency_type' : 'manage',
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             'No',
			             '職能',
			             '等級',
			             '評鑑者',
			             '評鑑方法',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:0 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'No' ,
			             name:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             width:30 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'center' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'職能' ,
			             name:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             width:180 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'等級' ,
			             name:'Level' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Level' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑者' ,
			             name:'Evaluator' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Evaluator' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑方法' ,
			             name:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             width:300 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 230,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#classevaluationtable_competencymanage_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "classevaluationtable_competencymanage_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencymanage/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'classevaluationtable_competencymanage_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencymanage/',
			add:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"新增評鑑關係",
				bclass:"add",
				body:"/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyedit/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			edit:{
				name:"編輯",
				title:"編輯評鑑關係",
				bclass:"edit",
				body:"/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyedit/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"刪除評鑑關係",
				bclass:"delete",
				body:"/hrd/function/delete/delete_competency_model.php",

		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("classevaluationtable_competencymanage_list", {
			url : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencymanage/pageList.html',
			postData : {
				'competency_type' : 'manage',
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             'No',
			             '職能',
			             '等級',
			             '評鑑者',
			             '評鑑方法',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:0 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'No' ,
			             name:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             width:30 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'center' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationRelationID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'職能' ,
			             name:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             width:180 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationTableTitle' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'等級' ,
			             name:'Level' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Level' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑者' ,
			             name:'Evaluator' ,
			             width:70 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'Evaluator' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'評鑑方法' ,
			             name:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             width:300 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'EvaluationMethod' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 230,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#classevaluationtable_competencymanage_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "classevaluationtable_competencymanage_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencymanage/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'classevaluationtable_competencymanage_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencymanage/',
			add:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"新增評鑑關係",
				bclass:"add",
				body:"/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyedit/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			edit:{
				name:"編輯",
				title:"編輯評鑑關係",
				bclass:"edit",
				body:"/hrd/classevaluationtable/competencyedit/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"刪除評鑑關係",
				bclass:"delete",
				body:"/hrd/function/delete/delete_competency_model.php",

	<input type="hidden" name="empId" value="F39BA5B7-0F25-492B-AB6B-7FFC132EB351" />
	<div id="tab1">

		<table id="report_setting_list"></table>
		<div id="report_setting_pager1"></div>
	</div>
</body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("report_setting_list", {
			url : '/hrd/report/setting/pageList.html',
			postData : {
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             'No',
			             'Title',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:0 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'No' ,
			             name:'GradingType' ,
			             width:30 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'center' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'GradingType' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'Title' ,
			             name:'GradingTypeTitle' ,
			             width:700 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'GradingTypeTitle' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 450,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#report_setting_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "report_setting_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/report/setting/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'report_setting_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/report/setting/',
			add:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"新增培訓教材",
				bclass:"add",
				body:"/hrd/training/material/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			edit:{
				name:"編輯",
				title:"編輯培訓教材",
				bclass:"edit",
				body:"/hrd/training/material/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"刪除培訓教材",
				bclass:"delete",
				body:"/hrd/function/delete/delete_competency_model.php",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
		});

	});

function button_obj()
{
	this.title = "Default";



}


</script>

	<input type="hidden" name="empId" value="F39BA5B7-0F25-492B-AB6B-7FFC132EB351" />
	<div id="tab1">

		<table id="competency_class_list"></table>
		<div id="competency_class_pager1"></div>
	</div>
</body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("competency_class_list", {
			url : '/hrd/competency/class/pageList.html',
			postData : {
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             '級數',
			             '職能分級備註',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:35 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'級數' ,
			             name:'ClassID' ,
			             width:30 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'center' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'ClassID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'職能分級備註' ,
			             name:'CompetencyClassMemo' ,
			             width:700 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'CompetencyClassMemo' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 450,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#competency_class_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "competency_class_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/competency/class/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'competency_class_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/competency/class/',
			add:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"新增職能級數",
				bclass:"add",
				body:"/hrd/competency/level/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			edit:{
				name:"編輯",
				title:"編輯職能級數",
				bclass:"edit",
				body:"/hrd/competency/level/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"刪除職能級數",
				bclass:"delete",
				body:"/hrd/function/delete/delete_competency_model.php",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
		});

	});

function button_obj()
{
	this.title = "Default";



}


</script>

157:<script type="text/javascript" src="/hrd/Framework/little2.function.js"></script>

<body id="body_competency_class_list">
	<input type="hidden" name="empId" value="F39BA5B7-0F25-492B-AB6B-7FFC132EB351" />
	<div id="tab1">

		<table id="competency_class_list"></table>
		<div id="competency_class_pager1"></div>
	</div>
</body>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("competency_class_list", {
			url : '/hrd/competency/class/pageList.html',
			postData : {
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             '級數',
			             '職能分級備註',
			            ],
			colModel : [
			            {
			             display:'ID' ,
			             name:'key' ,
			             width:35 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:true ,
			             index:'key' ,
			             hidden:true ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'級數' ,
			             name:'ClassID' ,
			             width:30 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'center' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'ClassID' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			            {
			             display:'職能分級備註' ,
			             name:'CompetencyClassMemo' ,
			             width:700 ,
			             sortable:true ,
			             align:'left' ,
			             hide:false ,
			             index:'CompetencyClassMemo' ,
			             hidden:false ,
			            },
			],
			autowidth : true,
			height : 450,
			multiselect : true,
			toolbar : [ true, "top" ],
			pager : '#competency_class_pager1'
		});



		jzsoft.grid.inlineMenu({
			grid : "",
			paper : "competency_class_pager1",
			baseUrl : '/hrd/competency/class/',
			saveService : 'saveOrUpdate.html',
			delService : '',
		});


		jzsoft.grid.newBarMenu({
			gridId : 'competency_class_list',
			baseUrl : '/hrd/competency/class/',
			add:{
				name:"新增",
				title:"新增職能級數",
				bclass:"add",
				body:"/hrd/competency/level/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			edit:{
				name:"編輯",
				title:"編輯職能級數",
				bclass:"edit",
				body:"/hrd/competency/level/edit.html?type=&method=",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
			delete:{
				name:"刪除",
				title:"刪除職能級數",
				bclass:"delete",
				body:"/hrd/function/delete/delete_competency_model.php",
 		   		data:{},
 		   		height:parseInt(),
 		   		width:parseInt()
			},
		});

	});

function button_obj()
{
	this.title = "Default";



}


</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("competency_class_list", {

<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function() {
		//function(id, options, menup)
		jzsoft.grid("ability_list_list", {
			url : '/hrd/ability/list/pageList.html',
			postData : {
			},
			colNames : [
			             'ID',
			             'No',
			             '職能分級備註',
			             '職能內涵描述',
			            ],

			             display:'ID' ,

			             hide:true ,

			             hidden:true ,
			            },

			             display:'No' ,

			             width:30 ,

		});

				'competency_type' : 'C',
			},

			             display:'職能項目名稱' ,
			             name:'CompetencyTitle' ,
			             width:30 ,

			             align:'left' ,

			            },

			             display:'定義' ,

		});
